data.description:
Check out 315 Miles #C located near the heart of historic Livingston, Montana!
Welcome the sunrise through your living room window as the sun climbs Livingston Peak and paints the sky pink and orange each morning. The living space and kitchen provide a comfortable space to unwind and relax, and the vaulted ceilings create an open yet welcoming feel as you walk in through the front door. This larger unit offers two bedrooms and two full bathrooms with tons of storage space in each room, including crawl space access in the primary. A single car detached garage also provides more storage for all of your outdoor gear or projects! This unit has lovely curb appeal with the landscaped front lawn and Yellowstone river rock in the two parking spots. Enjoy the perks of low maintenance living as the HOA fees cover lawn maintenance, snow removal, and all exterior maintenance. Located only 5 minutes from the hospital, downtown shopping, Livingston schools, and the Yellowstone River. This condo would be a wonderful place to make Livingston your home!
